          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "寻梦归来自掩门。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "开门来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "晴雯",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是谁呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "连我的声音都听不出来了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "晴雯",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "噢，宝二爷回来啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（晴雯上，开门，贾宝玉进门，晴雯关门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛宝钗",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛宝钗上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛宝钗",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "庭皋向晚日昏黄，"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛宝钗",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "阵阵东风拂柳塘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛宝钗",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "新来燕子借画梁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛宝钗",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "小步茅尘绣鞋香。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛宝钗",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "行过了小桥"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛宝钗",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "抬头望，"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛宝钗",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "怡红院落在哪厢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛宝钗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奴、薛宝钗。春倦无聊，因此要看看宝兄弟，借些诗词消遣。来此已是“怡红"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛宝钗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "院”，待我来扣门。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛宝钗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，开门来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛宝钗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "落花无主春骀宕"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛宝钗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "含情迤逦穿花障"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "隔帘花影动，疑是玉人来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "落花无主春骀宕"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "含情迤逦穿花障"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "门外是哪个？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛宝钗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "连我的声音都听不出来了么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来是宝姐姐来了，待我亲自开门。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛宝钗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有劳了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾宝玉开门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姐姐请进！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛宝钗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛宝钗进门，贾宝玉关门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，姐姐光降，不胜荣幸之至。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛宝钗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这几日林妹妹可曾来过呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不曾来，想必是又恼了我了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛宝钗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "见着她的时候，赔个礼儿也就是了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是啊，赔个礼儿也就完了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛宝钗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兄弟，可有什么新诗新词，借来消遣。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "现有一绝妙好词在此，姐姐请看。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛宝钗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一同看来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛宝钗、贾宝玉同看诗，薛宝钗唱一段昆曲。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛宝钗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "外面风大，将窗儿关上了吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "关上了吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾宝玉关窗，贾宝玉、薛宝钗同下。）"
        }
      ],
