    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "林黛玉",
        "紫鹃"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（林黛玉上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "长安三月踏春阳，处处春阳总断肠。红瘦绿肥人寂寞，杜鹃声里吊余芳。"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奴、林黛玉。幼失怙恃，多蒙外祖母史太君抚养，寄居在荣国贾府之中。诸姑"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "春光好都付与工愁善病，"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "落红成阵，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（林黛玉弹琴。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎！"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "这焦桐却为何弹不成声？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（林黛玉看书。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "偏偏翻到这里来了，“良辰美景奈何天，赏心乐事谁家院？”这不是杜丽娘伤"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "这几日闷恹恹春将人困，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（林黛玉哭。紫鹃上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "紫鹃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我们姑娘又在这儿哭哪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "送春么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "紫鹃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "春到哪里去了，怎么不叫它回来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "紫鹃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "春去无言，叫我哪儿去找哪？"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么，春去无言？"
        },
        {
          "character": "紫鹃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎，紫鹃，安顿花锄，我要葬花去了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "紫鹃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "外面春风似剪，姑娘不去也罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你看，花谢花飞，一片片沾泥随水，世间薄命的人儿还不是与落花一样么？快"
        },
        {
          "character": "紫鹃",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（紫鹃下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "扫香帚贮红囊花锄一柄，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（紫鹃拿花锄上，交林黛玉。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "去到那沁芳桥葬玉埋春。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（林黛玉下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "紫鹃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想我们姑娘与宝二爷，从小就在一块儿长大，彼此十分相爱。他们的年纪一天"
        },
        {
          "character": "紫鹃",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "两情只要能常久，何必朝朝暮暮愁！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（紫鹃下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "林黛玉→紫鹃",
          "turns": 7
