    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "贾宝玉"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾宝玉上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "昨夜晚怨东风无端蹂躏，"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小生、贾宝玉。今日到此，一来是赴饯花盛会，二来得罪了林妹妹，等她到来，"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我这里扫残红独穿花径，"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你看梨花飘雪，柳絮飞棉。倘若俺林妹妹看见，一定是格外伤感。待俺将落花"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾宝玉扫花。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "远望一个女子，隐约行过花丛，想必是林妹妹来了。俺不免闪在一旁，听她说"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "隔林听燕语，掬水奠花魂。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾宝玉下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 7,
          "唱": 1,
          "白": 1
        },
