    {
      "scene_index": 4,
      "label": "第四场",
      "characters_present": [
        "林黛玉",
        "紫鹃",
        "贾宝玉"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（林黛玉上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "碧云天芳草地蜂愁蝶怨，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾宝玉暗上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来此已是葬花之所。这香冢之旁是哪个有心人替我扫了一堆花瓣，莫非就是那"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "反二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "反二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "林黛玉把花锄无限凄怆，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（林黛玉哭。贾宝玉哭。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "人家都道我是个痴子，听那边厢又有啼哭之声，难道还有个痴子不成么？待我"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（林黛玉回头看。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我道是谁，原来是那狠心短命的——"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（林黛玉走。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妹妹不要走。说完一句话，大家撩开手，好是不好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宝二爷，有什么吩咐？"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "话是有一句，不知道当讲不当讲？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（林黛玉欲走。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，既有今日，何必当初！"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这句话倒要问问你，今日怎么样？当初又是怎么样？"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "当初我与妹妹是怎样的好法：一同起坐，一同吃饭，一同玩耍；我有爱吃的东"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾宝玉、林黛玉对哭、对看。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你不要在这里骗我，还是请回去把那门关上吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，妹妹，这是哪里说起，我一点也不明白呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "昨晚我偶过“怡红院”，你为什么闭门不理？"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妹妹，实在无有此事。"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "还说无有此事，人家站在门外，连腿都站酸了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妹妹要是不信，我就跪下来赌咒！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾宝玉跪。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "皇天在上，我宝玉若有半句虚言，罚我掉在水里，变个大大的乌龟。等妹妹百"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（林黛玉笑。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "或是丫鬟、老妈子不好，不起来开门也是有的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丫鬟、老妈子不好，待我回去重重地责罚她们。"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是要责罚责罚才是。今日得罪了我不要紧，倘若得罪了什么宝姑娘，那就闹大"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "她又提起宝姐姐来了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这香冢之旁一堆花瓣，是你扫来的么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，看将起来，还是他才有这样的心情啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "你我问春春不管，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（林黛玉、贾宝玉同哭。紫鹃上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "紫鹃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，宝二爷也在这哪？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾宝玉、林黛玉忙拭泪。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "紫鹃姐姐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "紫鹃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姑娘，老太太等您吃饭哪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将花锄带了回去！"
        },
        {
          "character": "紫鹃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（紫鹃下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "流水落花春去也，"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "独留青冢向黄昏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "紫鹃",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姑娘来吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "噢，来了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（林黛玉、贾宝玉同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（完）"
        }
